						<div class="postbody">Tip: If your levels are 12 metatiles tall (as in the GIF example above), you can calculate six bytes of attributes (one for each set of four metatiles in the strip), set the PPU to +32, and write bytes 0 and 4, then 1 and 5, then 2, then 3.</div>

